<lb n="0491c07"/><head type="no">No. 1330</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0491c08"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0491027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>囉&CB00085;拏說救療小兒疾病經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0491c09"/>
<lb n="0491c10"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0491028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（宋）＋西【明】</note><app n="0491028"><lem>西</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">宋西</rdg></app>天譯經三藏朝散大夫試光祿卿
<lb n="0491c11"/>明教大師<note n="0491029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔臣〕－【明】</note><app n="0491029"><lem>臣</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>法賢奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0491c12"/><p>爾時囉&CB00085;拏。觀於世間一切小兒。從其初生
<lb n="0491c13"/>至十二歲。並在幼稚癡騃之位。神氣未足鬼
<lb n="0491c14"/>魅得便。有十二曜母鬼遊行世間。於晝夜分
<lb n="0491c15"/>常伺其便。或因眠睡或獨行坐。於此之際現
<lb n="0491c16"/>作種種差異之相。驚怖小兒令其失常。&CB00078;取
<lb n="0491c17"/>精氣。因成疾病遂至<note n="0491030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">殤＝傷【宋】【元】</note><app n="0491030"><lem>殤</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">傷</rdg></app>夭。我見是事深所哀
<lb n="0491c18"/>愍。我今為說十二曜母鬼。執魅小兒年月時
<lb n="0491c19"/>分所患疾狀。及說大明救療之法。乃至作法
<lb n="0491c20"/>出生祭祀儀則。若復有人聞我所說。有疾患
<lb n="0491c21"/>者時持明人。依於我法而作救療發至誠者。
<lb n="0491c22"/>定獲輕<note n="0491031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB04387;＝瘧</note><note n="0491031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB04387;＝瘧【unknown】</note><app n="0491031"><lem>&CB04387;</lem><rdg wit="【unknown】" resp="Taisho">瘧</rdg></app>安樂吉祥。十二曜母鬼名者所謂
<lb n="0491c23"/>摩怛哩難那<note place="inline">一</note>蘇難那<note place="inline">二</note>哩<note n="0491032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝縛【三】</note><note n="0491032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00085;＝縛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0491032"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">縛</rdg></app>帝<note place="inline">三</note>目佉曼尼
<lb n="0491c24"/>迦<note place="inline">四</note>尾拏&CB00619;<note place="inline">五</note>設俱&CB00135;<note place="inline">六</note>布多曩<note place="inline">七</note>輸瑟迦<note place="inline">八</note>阿
<lb n="0491c25"/>哩也迦<note place="inline">九</note>染婆迦<note place="inline">十</note>必&CB00619;&CB00457;砌迦<note place="inline">十一</note>塞健馱<note place="inline">十
<lb n="0491c26"/>二</note>。</p>
<lb n="0491c27"/><p>如是等十二曜母鬼。執魅小兒為求祭祀。我
<lb n="0491c28"/>今各各說其執魅相狀。若復小兒於初生日
<lb n="0491c29"/>初生月初生年被執魅者。是摩怛哩難那母
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1330.0492a" n="0492a"/>
<lb n="0492a01"/>鬼所執。其小兒先患寒熱。身體瘦弱漸漸乾
<lb n="0492a02"/>枯。心神荒亂身常顫掉。啼哭不食者。持明人
<lb n="0492a03"/>於二河岸取土。作患小兒像。於四方曼拏羅
<lb n="0492a04"/>內。面西安小兒像。復於曼拏羅設種種香華。
<lb n="0492a05"/>及白色飲食乃至酒肉等。復設七座幢燃七
<lb n="0492a06"/>盞燈。復用白芥子野狐糞&CB00339;兒糞安<note n="0492001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悉＝息【明】＊</note><app n="0492001"><lem>悉</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">息</rdg></app>香蛇
<lb n="0492a07"/>皮。以如是等藥用黃牛酥。同和為香燒薰小
<lb n="0492a08"/>兒。復用&CB03103;麻油麻荊子。或用葉及蓽茇羅樹
<lb n="0492a09"/>葉&CB00085;囉迦藥。如是五藥以水煎之沐浴小兒。
<lb n="0492a10"/>即誦大明。加持如上曼拏羅中祭食及種種
<lb n="0492a11"/>物。誦大明曰。</p>
<lb n="0492a12"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>曩謨囉<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;拏<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">一</note>怛賴<note place="inline">二合</note>路枳也<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0492a13"/>合</note>尾<note n="0492002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">捺＝&CB00706;【宋】【元】</note><app n="0492002"><lem>捺</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&CB00706;</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>&CB00425;拏<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">二</note>賀曩&CB00085;日哩<note place="inline">二合<note n="0492003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【三】</note><note n="0492003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔引〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0492003"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0492a14"/>拏<note place="inline">三</note>沒囉<note place="inline">二合</note>憾摩<note place="inline">二合</note>難&CB00135;曩<note place="inline">四</note>摩<note place="inline">引</note>哩迦<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0492a15"/>嚕閉拏<note place="inline">五</note>摩<note place="inline">引</note>怛哩<note place="inline">二合</note>難那<note place="inline">引六</note>&CB00085;囉&CB00085;囉<note place="inline">七</note>
<lb n="0492a16"/>輸瑟迦<note place="inline">二合</note>輸瑟迦<note place="inline">二合八</note>捫左捫左<note place="inline">九</note>俱摩<note place="inline">引</note>囉
<lb n="0492a17"/><note n="0492004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">崗＝岡【明】＊</note><app n="0492004"><lem>崗</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">岡</rdg></app>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十</note></p>
<lb n="0492a18"/><p>如是誦大明加持已出於城外。以日中時面
<lb n="0492a19"/>東。祭摩怛哩難那母鬼。所有祭食香華等物
<lb n="0492a20"/>隨處棄擲。所患小兒速得除瘥。</p>
<lb n="0492a21"/><p>復次小兒於初生後。第二日第二月第二年
<lb n="0492a22"/>得患者。是蘇難那母鬼所執。其小兒先患寒
<lb n="0492a23"/>熱作荒亂相。合眼不食手足<note n="0492005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">畜＝搐【明】＊</note><app n="0492005"><lem>畜</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">搐</rdg></app>搦腹內疼痛
<lb n="0492a24"/>吐逆喘息者。持明人當用米粉一斗。作病小
<lb n="0492a25"/>兒像面西。安曼拏羅中。復於曼拏羅設種種
<lb n="0492a26"/>上妙香華飲食及酒肉等。復用白色幢四座
<lb n="0492a27"/>燃燈四盞。復用安<app type="＊" source="0492001"><lem>悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">息</rdg></app>香蒜蛇皮白芥子&CB00339;兒
<lb n="0492a28"/>糞酥。同和為香燒薰小兒。又同前用五藥水
<lb n="0492a29"/>沐浴小兒。即誦大明。加持如上曼拏羅中祭
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1330.0492b" n="0492b"/>
<lb n="0492b01"/>食及種種物即說大明曰。</p>
<lb n="0492b02"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>曩謨囉<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;拏<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">一</note>怛賴<note place="inline">二合</note>路枳也<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0492b03"/>合</note>尾捺囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>波拏<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">二</note>贊捺囉<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>娑
<lb n="0492b04"/>馱哩尼<note place="inline">三</note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00942;多賀娑多<note place="inline">二合引</note>野<note place="inline">四</note>賀曩
<lb n="0492b05"/>賀曩<note place="inline">五</note>那賀那賀<note place="inline">六</note>怛哩<note place="inline">二合</note>輸&CB00619;曩努瑟吒
<lb n="0492b06"/><note place="inline">二合</note>屹囉<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引七</note>&CB00135;訖哩<note place="inline">二合</note>多野&CB00135;訖哩多
<lb n="0492b07"/>野<note place="inline">八</note>祖沙野祖沙野<note place="inline"><note n="0492006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">九＝引【明】</note><app n="0492006"><lem>九</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">引</rdg></app></note>賀曩賀曩<note place="inline">十</note>蘇難那捫
<lb n="0492b08"/>左捫左<note place="inline">十一</note>俱摩<note place="inline">引</note>囉<app type="＊" source="0492004"><lem>崗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">岡</rdg></app>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十二</note></p>
<lb n="0492b09"/><p>如是誦大明加持已出於城外。以<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" cf1="K34_p0413b02">戌</lem><rdg wit="【大】">戍</rdg></app>時面西。
<lb n="0492b10"/>祭蘇難那母鬼。所有祭食香華等物隨處棄
<lb n="0492b11"/>之。所患小兒速得除瘥。</p>
<lb n="0492b12"/><p>復次小兒於初生後。第三日第三月第三年
<lb n="0492b13"/>得患者。是哩&CB00085;帝母鬼所執。其小兒忽然驚
<lb n="0492b14"/>悸。叫呼啼哭身體疼痛。寒熱無睎Y面顫動。
<lb n="0492b15"/>顧視自身漸漸羸弱。不思飲食以至枯瘦者。
<lb n="0492b16"/>持明人當用種種上味肉食及生肉生魚酒
<lb n="0492b17"/>等。設紅色<note n="0492007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">憧＝幢【三】</note><note n="0492007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">憧＝幢【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0492007"><lem>憧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">幢</rdg></app>八座燃燈八盞。復用尾螺樹葉
<lb n="0492b18"/>安息香蛇皮蒜&CB00339;兒糞白芥子等。用酥同和
<lb n="0492b19"/>燒薰小兒。及同前五藥煎以水。沐浴小兒即
<lb n="0492b20"/>誦大明。加持如上曼拏羅中祭食及種種物。
<lb n="0492b21"/>即說大明曰。</p>
<lb n="0492b22"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>曩謨囉<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;拏<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">一</note><note n="0492008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">捺＝&CB00706;【明】＊</note><app n="0492008"><lem>捺</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00706;</rdg></app>舍&CB00085;那曩<note place="inline">二</note>贊
<lb n="0492b23"/><app type="＊" source="0492008"><lem>捺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&CB00706;</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>娑<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">三</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00942;
<lb n="0492b24"/>多賀娑多<note place="inline">二合引</note>野<note place="inline">四</note>賀曩賀曩<note place="inline">五</note>那賀那賀<note place="inline">六</note>摩
<lb n="0492b25"/>哩那<note place="inline">二合</note>野摩哩那<note place="inline">二合</note>野<note place="inline">七</note>努瑟吒<note place="inline">二合</note>屹囉
<lb n="0492b26"/><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00780;<note place="inline">八</note>謨吒野謨吒野娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引九</note></p>
<lb n="0492b27"/><p>如是誦大明加持已出於城外。以<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" cf1="K34_p0413c02">戌</lem><rdg wit="【大】">戍</rdg></app>時面向
<lb n="0492b28"/>北。祭哩&CB00085;帝母鬼。所有祭食種種物等隨處
<lb n="0492b29"/>棄之。所患小兒速得除瘥。</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1330.0492c" n="0492c"/>
<lb n="0492c01"/><p>復次小兒於初生後。第四日第四月第四年
<lb n="0492c02"/>得患者。是目佉曼尼迦母鬼所執。其小兒先
<lb n="0492c03"/>患寒熱。欬<note n="0492009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01486;＝嗽【明】＊</note><app n="0492009"><lem>&CB01486;</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">嗽</rdg></app>吐逆身顫垂頭。啼哭手搔兩目
<lb n="0492c04"/>顧視人面。不思飲食饒大小便者。持明人當
<lb n="0492c05"/>於河兩岸取土。作病小兒像。面西安曼拏羅
<lb n="0492c06"/>內。復設種種香華。及生熟肉食并酒果等。又
<lb n="0492c07"/>用紅色幢四座燃四盞燈。復用兜羅子蛇皮
<lb n="0492c08"/>&CB00339;兒糞牛角虎爪白芥子等。同和為香燒薰
<lb n="0492c09"/>小兒。復用同前五藥水沐浴小兒。即誦大明。
<lb n="0492c10"/>加持如上曼拏羅中祭食及種種物。即說大
<lb n="0492c11"/>明曰。</p>
<lb n="0492c12"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>曩謨<note place="inline">一</note>沒囉<note place="inline">二合</note>憾摩<note place="inline">二合引</note>尾&CB00425;努<note place="inline">二合</note>摩
<lb n="0492c13"/>呬濕&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉<note place="inline">二</note>塞剛<note place="inline">二合</note>那虎多<note place="inline">引</note>設曩<note place="inline">三</note>目
